                        "text": "So far my favorite meal in Japan and it could end up being the best meal of the entire trip!\n\nSumiyaki Unafuji\nMultiple locations throughout Japan\n\nUnagi is already one of my favorite Japanese dishes, and this is one of if not the best version of it I've ever had. Will absolutely go back and eat here again.\n\n#unagi #eel #japanesefood #japanfood #tokyo"
